{"tid":2251644,"cid":21,"subCid":5,"title":"[英國音樂] Little Mix 討論區 - 新專輯Confetti將於11月6日推出","createTime":"2020-10-21T02:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T03:17:31.000Z","uid":379538,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"398aa92cf355387e8b7f57a8ac4137d38f2593ef","tid":2251644,"uid":379538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjaorii.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwjaorii.jpg&h=53b38a76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nConfetti is the sixth studio album by Little Mix. It is scheduled for release on November 6, 2020 with &quot;Break Up Song&quot; as the lead single. It is the group's first album separate from their previous record label Syco.<br />\n<br />\nLittle Mix（簡稱LM，前身為Rhythmix）是英國女子音樂組合。<br />\n2011年8月19日於歌唱比賽The X Factor UK上出道。粉絲名稱為Mixer。<br />\n<br />\n2011年，Little Mix透過英國電視選秀節目《X Factor》（X音素），在客座評審兼歌手的Kelly Rowland措合下组成。同年12月11日，Little Mix正式成為The X Factor UK節目史上第一組冠軍團體，且是第一組晉級到前三強的全女子團體。<br />\n<br />\nJesy Nelson 潔希&middot;尼爾森 1991年6月14日（29歲） 主領舞、饒舌、Beatbox、街舞<br />\nLeigh AnnePinnock 雷伊&middot;安妮&middot;皮諾克 1991年10月4日（28歲） 主饒舌、中音<br />\nJade Thirlwall 潔德&middot;席爾沃 1992年12月26日（27歲） 低音、中音、中高音、舞蹈<br />\nPerrie Edwards 珮芮&middot;艾德華茲 1993年7月10日（27歲） 高音、吉他<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OQ_mw1N1Kyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOQ_mw1N1Kyw&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=9c0feb90\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OQ_mw1N1Kyw</a><br />\nLittle Mix - Not a Pop Song (Lyric Video)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gSMn9thX-yw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgSMn9thX-yw&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=b4053520\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gSMn9thX-yw</a><br />\nLittle Mix - Happiness (Lyric Video)"},{"pid":"7213f6dd136768d593d551c5bb2a6e46a4ce1855","tid":2251644,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:40:53.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n但連登好似冇乜<del>mixer</del> gorgey hun<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5e0fde61a361ecd8c4493d9aaa61d4d7183ce2","tid":2251644,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:50:53.000Z","msg":"上一張album退步左<br />\n無左個好fresh嘅感覺<br />\n希望今次有改善"},{"pid":"77b037c819f6a1b89481afcf1ba363da6b05c3a3","tid":2251644,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T16:53:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/56ZAe0yrbVM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F56ZAe0yrbVM&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=a59135be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/56ZAe0yrbVM</a>"},{"pid":"e872f2650473e9afaf392c3b82cbefd5eff8d87d","tid":2251644,"uid":149225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ad336f0d3fe63b8088ecb4107f1266a018a236","tid":2251644,"uid":379538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7213f6dd136768d593d551c5bb2a6e46a4ce1855","tid":2251644,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:40:53.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n但連登好似冇乜<del>mixer</del> gorgey hun<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:55:35.000Z","msg":"慢慢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46e59bb527b70ca2e0b7e14312aa8da047548ef","tid":2251644,"uid":379538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f5e0fde61a361ecd8c4493d9aaa61d4d7183ce2","tid":2251644,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T03:50:53.000Z","msg":"上一張album退步左<br />\n無左個好fresh嘅感覺<br />\n希望今次有改善"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:57:41.000Z","msg":"我個人都覺得LM5得幾首算真係好聽<br />\n其他就真係無乜特別<br />\n但總好過成日出埋啲罐頭抒情歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdb3da4f9b0fc538f05816ccc8044f5da085604","tid":2251644,"uid":379538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77b037c819f6a1b89481afcf1ba363da6b05c3a3","tid":2251644,"uid":34071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T16:53:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/56ZAe0yrbVM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F56ZAe0yrbVM&d=URyNnIoFf2HINYay4fd4QaQEQZ%2FBMmOowG797g%2FgSDo%3D&h=a59135be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/56ZAe0yrbVM</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T02:59:32.000Z","msg":"暫時嚟講Confetti幾首都唔錯<br />\n呢首我就嫌前奏麻麻 係咁dododododo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但中後都唔錯"},{"pid":"92a52287246cd28a67178ee6c7793e4ef3a103a6","tid":2251644,"uid":379538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T03:02:04.000Z","msg":"Little Mix LM5 - The Tour Film (2020)<br />\n21-11-2020 上映<br />\n97 分鐘<br />\n---(英文字幕)<br />\n<br />\n自2011年出道以來, Little Mix旋即成為最知名女團之一, 售出超過5千萬張唱片, 在Spotify 上擁有1700萬粉絲, 於Youtube 更有超過3億次點擊率｡<br />\n<br />\n在2019年推出第5張唱片&lsquo;LM5&rsquo;後, Perrie､ Jesy､Leigh-Anne及Jade 展開&lsquo;LM5 The Tour&rsquo;演唱會, 在歐洲超過40個舞台演出, 巡迴多個國家, 包括西班牙､意大利､德國及法國等｡ 整個巡迴演唱會不單售出超過40萬張門票, 於英國倫敦O2 體育館更有足足5場爆滿, 座無虛席! <br />\n<br />\nLittle Mix LM5 - The Tour Film (2020) 攝錄於倫敦地標O2體育館的最後一場演唱會, 邀請到 Stormzy 及Kamille 作表演嘉賓｡ Little Mix 更於演唱會中落力表演多首名曲如Shout Out to My Ex, Woman Like Me, Wings 及 Touch 等, 又唱又跳, Mixers 一定不會失望! <br />\n<br />\nLittle Mix LM5 - The Tour Film (2020)只於百老匯院線限量上映!<br />\n<br />\n下個21同22號全球戲院都有上佢哋演唱會電影<br />\n但全港只得2場 其中一場仲要就黎爆爆哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1345d